  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Water Treatment</div>
        <p>Understand the principles of physical, chemical, and biological water treatment processes.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/sustainable-water-infrastructure/water-and-wastewater-treatment" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Air Pollution Control</div>
        <p>Master the fundamentals of air quality management, emissions control, and monitoring.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/air-quality-management-process" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Solid Waste Management</div>
        <p>Learn about waste collection, processing, recycling, and disposal methods.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/landfills" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Environmental Impact Assessment</div>
        <p>Study methodologies for evaluating environmental impacts of projects and developments.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/nepa" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Hazardous Waste Management</div>
