        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/hw" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Environmental Remediation</div>
        <p>Learn about techniques for cleaning up contaminated sites and groundwater.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/remedytech" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Hydrology</div>
        <p>Study water cycle, watershed processes, and surface/groundwater interactions.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://water.usgs.gov/edu/hydrology.html" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Environmental Chemistry</div>
        <p>Explore chemical processes in air, water, and soil environments.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.acs.org/education/resources/undergraduate/chemistryincontext.html" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Renewable Energy Systems</div>
        <p>Master applications of solar, wind, and other renewable energy technologies.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.energy.gov/eere/renewables" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Climate Change Mitigation</div>
        <p>Learn techniques for reducing greenhouse gas emissions and carbon footprint.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/climate-change" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Environmental Microbiology</div>
        <p>Study microorganisms in environmental processes and treatment systems.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.asm.org/Articles/Policy/Environmental-Microbiology" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Sustainable Design</div>
        <p>Understand principles of green building, eco-design, and life cycle assessment.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/sustainability" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Environmental Modeling</div>
        <p>Explore computational models for environmental systems and processes.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/research/environmental-modeling" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Environmental Policy</div>
        <p>Learn about regulations, compliance, and policy frameworks for environmental protection.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/laws-regulations" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Ecological Engineering</div>
        <p>Study integration of ecological principles in environmental problem-solving.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.epa.gov/eco-research" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

